Games fanduel summary

Returns fanduel summary for specified game ids

get_games_fanduel_summary(game_ids = c(21700002, 21700003),
  nest_data = FALSE, return_message = TRUE)

Arguments

game_ids

vector of game ids
nest_data

if TRUE nests data
return_message

if T returns message

Value

a data_frame

See also

Other season: get_games_pbp_win_probablity

Other game: get_game_logs, get_games_box_scores, get_games_pbp_win_probablity

Examples

# NOT RUN {
get_games_fanduel_summary(game_ids = c(21700002, 21700003), nest_data = F, return_message = T)
# }
